<template>
  <form>
    <textarea placeholder="Write a comment..." :rows="3" require></textarea>
    <button>Submit</button>
  </form>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "CommentForm",
  props: {
    newCommentContent: {
      type: String,
      required: true
    },
    newReplyContent: ""
  }
}
</script>
